NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000

# PostgreSQL Database Configuration
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://youruser:yourpassword@localhost:5432/taskdb?schema=public"

# JWT Secret and Expiration
JWT_SECRET="your_jwt_secret_key_here_should_be_long_and_random"
JWT_ACCESS_EXPIRATION_MINUTES=30
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRATION_DAYS=30

# Redis Cache Configuration
REDIS_HOST=localhost
REDIS_PORT=6379
# REDIS_PASSWORD=your_redis_password_if_any

# API Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000 # 15 minutes (15 * 60 * 1000)
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100 # max 100 requests per 15 minutes
```

#### `Dockerfile`

```dockerfile